text.tspan: Pet owner watches indoor camera to monitor his dog.
He is busy all day, he couldn’t watch a camera.
After work he come home, found his dog is sick.
He bring him to hospital if he arrives little late, his dog will be die.
Pet owner frustrate and feel guilty.
